channel.title: Why do I lagg alot on Runescape? Help Me plz
channel.description: Hello all, I was wondering what the problem could be. When I start Eliteswitch and login in everything is all fast and stuff, but after atleast 10 or 15 mins of playing it just turns horrible like 14.4k dial up. Now before you ask and say things. I have dial-up(56k) but still i go alot faster then that what could be the problem. And i would get High-speed or DSL but its not availible where I live. Help me plz.

item.title: Why do I lagg alot on Runescape? Help Me plz

item.description:

[quote=“yeee_boi, post:8, topic:33063”]You answered your own question…DIAL UP!!! Dial up is the most slowest and primitive internet connection make your parents get yo high speed or wireless…[/quote] If you had read my first post then you would know that it isn’t availible where i live right now. Also i said that i wasnt really lagging before with my dial up, so its not because i got dial up.

Thank you for your replies,
